snippet.title: MONSTER HIGH: Ghoul Spirit - Announcement Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Sometimes THQ announces games withrubber purple 'extensions' as weapons and sometimes they get pre-teen girly games. You can't say they aren't diverse. Monster High Ghoul Spirit is out October 2011 on Wii and DS.

Visit: http://www.NoobFeed.com for more info.
